data.description: Welcome to a beautiful well maintained home located in Ontario. You are greeted with a homey front porch, with fruit trees providing some privacy; perfect for coffee in the mornings. This home is a good size home: 960 sqft, 6,032 sqft lot, three bedrooms, one bath, detached two car garage, alley access in the backyard with an automatic gate, and potential RV parking. Very cozy home with unique high wood ceilings. The closed off patio has a lot of potential, it can be used as a bonus game room, office, etc. This home is perfect for a growing family; conveniently close to the 10 fwy. You don't want to miss out!
